package org.cajeta.logging;

// Build-ready placeholder for the cajeta-logging public facade.
//
// The real API — structured loggers, JSONL appenders, the per-request system
// log, and the metrics bridge — is specified in docs/logging-spec.md and
// staged in plan/logging-plan.md. This stub exists so the library compiles to
// a .cja out of the box; replace it as the API lands.
